rows.label: tlk79000006_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I sense that His Majesty is not quite
himself of late.

rows.label: tlk79000006_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I cannot blame him, considering the
terrible events to which he has borne
witness...

rows.label: tlk79000006_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Though he tries not to show it,
I have come to understand the
workings of his heart.
